    "Later, more experimental validations were performed to compute the implemented network efficiency.",
    "Long et al.",
    "32 have implemented a GP algorithm to study the essential pHRI signal and it attained the angular increment of active joints as the outcome.",
    "Essential data for the validation were gathered by the torque sensor and also active joint of the angular position was computed using an optical position sensor.",
    "Later, the collected pHRI signals were managed with the Kalman smoother to accomplish better functions."
